name: Uh!Bodega
description: ¡Hola! Welcome to Uh!Bodega, a magical caribbean shop filled with spicy treats, colorful rare collectibles and chaotic magic stuff for your spells.  Feel free to look around and please don’t touch el gato, his name is Ónix and his kinda moody.   Uh!Bodega, Bodegatos and BodegaBaddies are all concepts of audiovisual artist UhCaribe and the CARIBverse.
